4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring 3 live online classes each week with a maximum class size of 16. Students build foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, focusing on cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. There's no prior experience required, and the course is available in both English and Spanish. Upon completion, participants receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by various institutions. For more information, visit: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop